com.isotrol.impe3.pms.gui.api.service
Interface ICategoriesServiceAsync

All Superinterfaces:
com.google.gwt.user.client.rpc.RemoteService
All Known Implementing Classes:
CategoriesController
public interface ICategoriesServiceAsync
extends com.google.gwt.user.client.rpc.RemoteService

GWT-RPC service for Categories. It is analog to com.isotrol.impe3.pms.api.CategoryService, but uses GWT-compatible types.

Author:
Andrei Cojocaru
